Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始我将作为奏同学的学业辅助宠物在这里学习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fad(200,0)\fn@方正黑体_GBK\pos(1180,358)\frx358\fry4\frz270.4}学业辅助宠物　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞠躬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哦哦哦哦哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学业辅助宠物是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个轻浮神搞的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱呢　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉　给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管那么多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏对我太无情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明明都是做过四十八手的关系了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四十八手？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：日本的谚语「人の噂も七十五日」 世间的传言不会超过75天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是七十五天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是《搔痒四十八手》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那么猥琐的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:01:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HF4F3B6&\3c&HCA7824&}①进入后宫时间\N被四个白名单学生(在校生)表白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFECCFD&\3c&H80287F&}②不久后就会发生非常爽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然两边都是好的选项
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我选项①的后宫时间
