Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说　奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家给了我好多点心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再给你一些点心　快来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正大家不久就会厌倦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来　到底什么时候才会开启后宫模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘草君　和你说几句话可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了　雪平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　是关于你用来处理你青春冲动的宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉小姐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说了啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听清吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有关你用来发泄性欲的宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉小姐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和刚才说的不一样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从一开始就是自慰宠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊够了　给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　富良野同学也要吃点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点心也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我要享用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈诶诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　你突然发什么神经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀　我只是在和甘草君做同样的事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是像这样　每晚揉着她的双乳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我自重一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你问问裘可拉本人不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实到底是怎样的呢　裘可拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　被他揉过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天早上一睁眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏就站着旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我柔软柔软　Q弹Q弹的地方　揉了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　我已经吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说那种老套的梦话了　快点起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不是那么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羡慕嫉妒恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}不…不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐　甘草　稍微揍一下你的脸可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐　甘草　稍微戳一下你的眼睛可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐　甘草　稍微买你几个器官可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说不是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀　他要揉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀　他要开始揉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀　他要狠狠揉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　各位女生　我只想问一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　其实也不是打心底讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你还算是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你的怪异反差行为太多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以老实说感觉很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是谢谢你们委婉的台词分工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是很喜欢奏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　你一开口反而会变得更麻烦所以还是闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说到底为什么瞒着我　突然出现在这个学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么　裘可…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀　小甘甘　不错的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看　很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我家的试制品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这　这真是划时代的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fad(0,2000)\pos(644,452)}裘可拉眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能让奏Ｘ奏这种事情变为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是不能抑制住心中的激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经知道了　赶紧取下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨　讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到　被看到内裤是这么令人害羞的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你还在在意之前的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs37}This is spats!\N{\r}这是紧身裤!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话无论怎样被看　都没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊　看啊　看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　还是快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊　一大早就是底裤　波波　自慰宠物什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的后宫时间到底什么时候才会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说今天早上的选项是咋回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上绝对选项中的内容都是最糟糕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再加上一个更糟糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说实际上只有一个选项
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔会有两边选项都一样糟糕的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会有一项稍好的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两边都是好选项的情况还是第一次出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和完成了解除诅咒任务有关？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了有人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在里面的是甘草君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么在找我　这里可是男厕所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘草君～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶诶　你　你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实呆着别动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了昨天的节目了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JTV？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了甘草君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看　那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生白名单里名列前茅的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西野学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等　甘草君～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也和我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊　为什么人好像变多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是男生白名单的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称作玫瑰野兽的笠间学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样是被称作甜点之王的石岗学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有全裸的帝王樱川学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「虽说是人气白名单里的学生的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也没说是女生哟」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样小学生似的歪理！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧　和我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交往吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊喔　奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和男生们一起组成的美妙后宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和各种激烈的摔跤时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　在四人中被几人爆菊花了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有被爆菊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛　无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有所期待的我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为选项对象的人事后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会失去事情前后的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆你菊花的那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该都忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了没有被爆菊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偶尔也作为过来人提点建议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而只是被限制了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能对其他人说起诅咒的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实　会头痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然完成了几个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除了诅咒本身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是留有相关的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你能说的也只有一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想全盘托出的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被阻挠的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得选项出现了微妙的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想关于这个问一下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为你完成了两个任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时候每完成一个任务就会逐渐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说　你问这么多的人不应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是那只小狗崽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是为了解除诅咒才呆在你身边的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是那样　但是她似乎失忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈　真没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时候的助手不但提供了相应的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其他方面也很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他去买炒面面包和啤酒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是个跑腿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只小狗崽　在家里是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完饭　无所事事　然后吃零食
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完饭　无所事事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　吃完饭　无所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对关键任务的帮助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有想要帮忙的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一点忙都帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会让那种家伙住下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏　我的大脑正在渴求着甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛　我今天也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么多种类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人选择困难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊　如果是这种选项的话非常欢迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ｈｅｌｌｏ　ｈｅｌｌｏ　奏君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天在学校怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成　发生了比平时更刺激的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把电源也关了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都可以做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是神嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　奏君想的事我大概都明白哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得神就要有神样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啪啪地把诅咒解除了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说　这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊　比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让掉落的苹果悬在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是可以办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　我也觉得你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有　奏君的电脑里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫「超咸湿」的文件夹里的女子的图片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部变成绦虫之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可怕耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说谁会取那么显眼的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道真正的名称是「通往哲学家之路」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　也有我没办法出手的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是负责这部分的神把自己独创的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中途强加进来而产生的扭曲真理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　在你们的世界就叫做诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你无法干涉诅咒和任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在给我发绝对选项和任务的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底又是何方神圣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答得这么快！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实　那位宅在家的前任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎也没有完全把握诅咒的详情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是接手呢　还是扔了烂摊子给我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　什么　真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}喂　喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1}{\pos(640,358)\c&HF4F3B6&\3c&HCA7824&}①看下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1}{\pos(642,606)\c&HFECCFD&\3c&H80287F&}②不看下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像说是在第二十二世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙爆破炸弹快要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说我还不介入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎会变得很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样了　拜拜　ｂａｂｙ～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛　宇宙爆破炸弹什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏　电话讲完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯啊　结果还是没有新情报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛　先来尝尝甜饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来放松一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底吃了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜食是装在另一个胃里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本没吃甜食之外的东西吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才奏大人讲电话的时候　我还吃了仙贝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在自豪些什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以坐在你旁边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么总是那么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　只要我对奏有用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种态度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能对真正喜欢的人才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　我最喜欢奏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你所说的那种喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是更复杂意义上的喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢还分种类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呀　觉得自己一天比一天更喜欢奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等　等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事　刚才的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗　对了　这家伙是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　狗　坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会让那家伙长住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　没什么　趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的　为什么会让这家伙长住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn@方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fscx162\fscy193\frz277\pos(572,294)}新入生欢迎会\N演出节目讨论会议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年惯例的新生欢迎会的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于本班的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见的请举手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有有有 我想跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有想演戏剧的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个还不如搞乐队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　雪平同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合掌怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:26.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：日语中「合掌」和「合唱」发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起唱歌似乎也挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌？　你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　刚才你说合唱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是　双手合十　幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这　这个合掌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是单纯的双关语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是大家来找茬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的人都在台上拼命地合掌礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手掌被胶水粘上的无信仰的家伙混在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让观众把那人找出来的新游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企划名是「寻找浆糊小子」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用写也行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有　我有我有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上我正在开发的这个的话　会有有趣的事发生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们班的女生大家都穿上泳衣站在台上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让观众全员都戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做了　会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能透视～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小肠　大肠　十二指肠　直肠全都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企划名就叫「脏器博览会雅」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要给人很文雅的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不用写也行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　裘可拉酱　请说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从昨天的事得到了启发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生们穿着泳衣摔跤　我想会很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便受启发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎　怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉酱这么说的话　试试也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是裘可拉酱的请求嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不讨厌那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！　大家太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说　最后那个是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　呜吼　来摔跤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么擅自起了标题！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微打扰下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧　那个帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生白名单第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　是学生会副会长　狮子守想牙前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宴大姐头　能稍微借我点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫我大姐头　要说多少次才明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被我勒死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　好像是　抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是甘草奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位就是美男狮子前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说…狮子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看名字叫狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说叫「狮子假面」比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：日语中「狮子」的发音是「しし」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘻嘻嘻嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆把狮子藏起来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是富野良
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐垫一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦　不喜欢美男狮子学长这个称呼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那叫美狮前辈怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　这个感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用平假名写「いけおん」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在中间加上☆变成「いけ☆おん」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉马上就会火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这是为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘草奏同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游王子讴歌同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪平富野良同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了邀请你们三位参加欢迎会的主要项目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生对抗而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会会长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连续三期称霸女生白名单第一位的女帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑白院清罗前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对抗战？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白名单5名和「五黑」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自选出几名男女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在台上进行一对一的对决项目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一提　白名单的参加成员已经决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么要找我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡起来就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(1005,402)\frz18.5}中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(275,350)\frz334.5}中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(670,125)\frz351}中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀　大家都中大奖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中奖是指…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　参加人员的抽签
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了　大家都很走运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧身裤　紧身裤～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和紧身裤没关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对抗战　倒过来读也是　对抗战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法念吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了　还有一名是三年级的梦岛乌同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦岛乌同学是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是学园中屈指可数的怪人的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？　还有一人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一位是特别名额
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家帮忙选出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糊弄过去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:20:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糊弄过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是很明白　不过加油啊奏～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么擅自跑去小卖部了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀　你就是学业辅助宠物裘可拉同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像人偶一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　真的好像不是人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位　打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说我们是成员了　成员～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　你们差不多该回到座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让参加对抗战的全部女生对你说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期限是5月31日星期五对抗战结束之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:31.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an3}どこかで僕を呼んだ 姿見えない声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:31.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an7}不知在何方呼唤着我 不见踪影的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:40.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an3}脳裏をよぎった デジャブ キミと重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:40.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an7}闪过脑内的既视感 与你重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:46.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an3}廻りだした 光と影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:46.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an7}交相错映 光和影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:52.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an3}夢の場所へ 走り出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:52.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an7}朝着梦之场所奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:57.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an3}始まりの 合図を奏でて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:57.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an7}奏响初始的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:01.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an3}イタズラな 時を恐れず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:01.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an7}不惧时光的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:07.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an3}運命の 導く風に乗れば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:07.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an7}乘上命运的引导之风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:17.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an3}キミと 泣きたいほど 眩しい 空が見える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:17.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1\an7}与你同见催人泪下的耀眼天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFECCFD&\3c&H80287F&}②发生非常爽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选非常爽的事情真是正解啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么美妙的事居然出现在我的人生里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今以来没有败给绝对选项
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生　这位患者的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:23:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很恶心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.61,0:24:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家觉得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是Afilia Saga
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.87,0:24:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的裘可拉很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说喊汪的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因为可爱就原谅她什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.73,0:24:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我很中意讴歌的紧身裤！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧身裤说起来有点昭和的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.47,0:24:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道　把背心说成夹克的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:26.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：法语「ｇｉｌｅｔ」，意为「西服背心」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　那个不是应该叫ｇｉｌｅｔ吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.03,0:24:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛　这个问题我们先不急不急～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　刚才那是双关语？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.31,0:24:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢　下回的「脑内喜剧」是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.29,0:24:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HF4F3B6&\3c&HCA7824&}①妹纸　出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.71,0:24:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFECCFD&\3c&H80287F&}②胃　消化不良
